channel.title: Background & LoginBox
channel.description: How do I make my background and Login Box Go to the original RuneScape ones? I remember in some Java file you could comment a line out to make a custom background and leave it if you wanted the background to be the original. Can you do this for the login box also? If so, please tell me where to do this. Or if not, please give me a link to a login box.
